layerGroup.name: AusEEZ_bathy_composite_multires_shallow
layerGroup.title: Hillshaded multi-resolution bathymetry composite for the Aus EEZ - style optimised for shelf (shallow) waters
layerGroup.abstractTxt: A multi-resolution depth-stratified continuous bathymetry surface for the Aus EEZ. This layer group displays bathymetry draped over hillshade, with a colour ramp stretch optimised for viewing shallower features in shelf (<200m) waters.
